  gem-c-title--margin-bottom-5">
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text ">
    Our governance
  </h1>
</div>

    </div>
    
    <div class="column-two-thirds">
      
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph ">
    HM Revenue and Customs (HMRC) is a non-ministerial department.
  </p>

      
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="grid-row ">
