<p>The Board is assisted by 4 further non-executives who serve on the Board’s committees:</p>

<ul>
  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/people/michael-hearty">Michael Hearty</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/people/diane-herbert">Diane Herbert</a></li>
